    <deftitle>Marelli IAW 8P.40 Peugeot 106 - Comparison Markup</deftitle>
    <description>Reverse-engineering XDF for Marelli IAW 8P.40 Peugeot 106. Version 0.54 removes obsolete MOD2 discovery aliases and redundant percent fuel-trim views, retains authoritative raw plus multiplier fuel views, and uses code-trace-based limiter, spark-bank, bypass-spark, and fast closed-loop fuel-correction names.</description>
    <author>OpenAI Codex</author>
