  <XDFCONSTANT uniqueid="0x2B8">
    <title>Expected Stack Top Word @ 0x916A</title>
    <description>Code-confirmed big-endian stack-top word. Reset loads SP from this address and the main-loop guard compares the saved SP against it at 0xD2F4. Stock value is 0x27FF. Firmware support, not a tuning calibration.</description>
