    <title>Checksum Service Enable Byte @ 0x916E</title>
    <description>Code-confirmed byte read at 0x5AD7 before each incremental checksum step. Zero bypasses accumulation and clears the checksum fault bit; stock value is 0xFF. Firmware/checksum support, not a tuning calibration.</description>
