  <XDFTABLE uniqueid="0x21C" flags="0x30">
    <title>Per-event Retard / Gain Candidate 1x19 @ 0x89F3</title>
    <description>Code-confirmed 0x2044-indexed vector stored to 0x20BC. MOD2 changes 16 of 19 cells. Current best role is per-event retard/gain candidate; grouped with ignition output/retard strategy.</description>
