  <XDFTABLE uniqueid="0x26C" flags="0x30">
    <title>Fuel Output Scheduler Scale vs $00CC Surplus $2040 1x9 @ 0x92FA</title>
    <description>Unsigned fuel-output scheduler-support vector indexed by internal $2040, where $2040 = max($00CC - 0x8000, 0) >> 4. D5DF interpolates this table with helper B2AB, multiplies the result by 40, and stores the 16-bit product to $2388. X labels are decimal $00CC display values for 0x8000, 0x9000, 0xA000, 0xB000, 0xC000, 0xD000, 0xE000, 0xF000, and 0xFFFF/end. Keep raw; this is scheduler timing support, not fuel quantity, and units remain internal until timer scale is proven.</description>
